{"title":"Release readiness: summary vs checklist","gitnotes":1,"type":"html","body":"<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<style>\n  :root { --bg:#0f1318; --fg:#e8ecf1; --muted:#7a8490; --accent:#a371f7; --card:#171c24; --border:#2b3240; --ok:#3fb950; }\n  * { box-sizing:border-box; }\n  body { font:15px/1.5 system-ui,sans-serif; background:var(--bg); color:var(--fg); margin:0; padding:1.5rem 2rem; max-width:46rem; }\n  h1 { font-size:1.28rem; margin:0 0 1rem; }\n  .switch { display:inline-flex; background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:8px; overflow:hidden; margin-bottom:1rem; }\n  .switch button { background:transparent; border:0; color:var(--muted); padding:.5rem 1rem; cursor:pointer; font:inherit; }\n  .switch button.on { background:var(--accent); color:#fff; }\n  .pane { display:none; }\n  .pane.on { display:block; }\n  ul.check { list-style:none; padding:0; margin:0; }\n  ul.check li { padding:.45rem 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); }\n  ul.check li::before { content:'\\2713'; color:var(--ok); margin-right:.55rem; }\n  .badge { display:inline-block; background:#238636; color:#fff; font-size:.75rem; padding:.15rem .5rem; border-radius:4px; margin-left:.5rem; }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<h1>Demo cache module — release gate</h1>\n<div class=\"switch\">\n  <button type=\"button\" class=\"on\" data-v=\"summary\">Summary</button>\n  <button type=\"button\" data-v=\"checklist\">Checklist</button>\n</div>\n<div id=\"summary\" class=\"pane on\">\n  <p>All four primitives (LRU, coalescer, TTL, barrel export) are in place with tests for the previously flagged TTL gaps. Safe to use for GitNotes screenshot demos.</p>\n  <p><a href=\"gitnotes:diff/examples/demo/cache/tests/ttl.test.ts#R5-R22\">TTL tests</a> close the TODO rows from the coverage note.<span class=\"badge\">ready</span></p>\n</div>\n<div id=\"checklist\" class=\"pane\">\n  <ul class=\"check\">\n    <li>LRU eviction + stats covered</li>\n    <li>Coalescer reject/retry regression covered</li>\n    <li>TTL lazy expiry + prune covered</li>\n    <li>Bench harness present</li>\n    <li>README composition example</li>\n    <li>index.ts re-exports stable API</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n<script>\ndocument.querySelectorAll('.switch button').forEach(function(btn) {\n  btn.addEventListener('click', function() {\n    document.querySelectorAll('.switch button').forEach(function(b){ b.classList.remove('on'); });\n    document.querySelectorAll('.pane').forEach(function(p){ p.classList.remove('on'); });\n    btn.classList.add('on');\n    document.getElementById(btn.dataset.v).classList.add('on');\n  });\n});\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>"}
